snippet.title: Durium Hospital Lost Tape 95 Teaser Trailer - Urbex "The Lost Tapes" Series
snippet.description:
Durium Hospital Lost Tape 95 - The third entry in "The Lost Tapes Series" Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/durium-hospital-lost-tape-95

Story: A tape was recovered from 1995 where a urban explorer enters the long abandoned Durium Hospital, the premise was active for over 30 years and served the city of Durium during its time. Unveil the stories hidden within these walls and try to survive against all odds. 

You've survived the "Incident Tapes" Series, now it's time to put your urban exploration skills and sanity to the ultimate test in "The Lost Tapes" Series.

VHS Urbex Found Footage "The Lost Tapes" FULL series out now - Buy now on Itch - 3 titles:
 Strongford Penitentiary Lost Tape 91 - https://azagamestudio.itch.io/strongford-penitentiary-lost-tape-91
 Moundville Factory Lost Tape 89 - https://azagamestudio.itch.io/moundville-factory-lost-tape-89
 Durium Hospital Lost Tape 95 - https://azagamestudio.itch.io/durium-hospital-lost-tape-95

Durium Hospital Lost Tape 95 is a VHS Urban Exploration Found Footage horror title with emphasis on atmosphere, unpredictability, realism and a non-linear design with multiple endings and outcomes.
